nodes.text: Star Wars: The Essential Atlas Online Companion/Update001

This table lists star system entries that were either modified in or added to the Star Wars: The Essential Atlas Online Companion as part of its first update at some point between August 28, 2009 and August 31, 2009. The table was published by Wookieepedia user Darth Culator on his user subpage on December 10, 2009, and copied here on February 19, 2020, per the version of October 18, 2019, in order to substitute as a backup version of the earliest unarchived version of the Online Companion.
